{"tid":1981464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"頌安邨強制隔離人士周圍走 引起街坊不滿 保安報警","createTime":"2020-04-20T16:22:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T18:05:16.000Z","uid":33719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"eeca5f8d461e4ec7c0abff3ac7162d24dab7e28d","tid":1981464,"uid":33719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T16:22:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/zhozunbo/videos/3100548406674825/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fzhozunbo%2Fvideos%2F3100548406674825%2F&d=1E6MrqGGcFSEGQF%2FdL0KzQX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=c1af4cc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/zhozunbo/videos/3100548406674825/</a>"},{"pid":"5af630231199d29099490a684fb54ff1b833f7ec","tid":1981464,"uid":33719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T16:24:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"759dd5a82a4eaf795d4544359801f4df3122645e","tid":1981464,"uid":90521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T16:25:31.000Z","msg":"究竟屌緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a951169fb88625b11acbdaec758198ed5b863a4b","tid":1981464,"uid":245250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"759dd5a82a4eaf795d4544359801f4df3122645e","tid":1981464,"uid":90521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T16:25:31.000Z","msg":"究竟屌緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T18:05:16.000Z","msg":"今晚件事係有街坊見到呢幾日頌安邨有強制隔離（帶手帶）人士周圍走 好不滿 就同保安起左衝突 然後係保安報警既<br />\n<br />\n然後有保安經理（已收工返左黎 片中黑色短袖）無禮貌回應 班呀伯對佢態度好不滿 衝突加劇<br />\n<br />\n後尾 黑警就話驅散 要3分鐘之內走 走左大部分人 主要淨返記者 <br />\n記者再問保安公司既人 佢地有講返係佢哋報警<br />\n但就話班啊伯係嬲左佢哋早排報警捉聚賭 所以今晚嘈得咁勁<br />\n<br />\n利申返呢間係新保安公司黎"}]}